text: Tami Noel is a retired United States Virgin Islands taekwondo athlete. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, where taekwondo was a demonstration sport, in the middleweight event. At the 1988 Pan American Taekwondo Championships she won the bronze medal in the -65 kg category. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:American martial artists Category:United States Virgin Islands Category:Olympians for the United States
